                                                            <div class="tab-pane" id="detailed-service-section-b">
                                                                <p>Our standard visa service. Before you apply for your
                                                                    visa yourself, we will consult with you to select
                                                                    the best visa option for your trip, advise you on
                                                                    the documents you need and check them to ensure they
                                                                    meet consulate requirements. We will also complete
                                                                    your application forms and prepare your application
                                                                    pack to allow you to apply and pay for your visa
                                                                    yourself with complete confidence.</p>

                                                                <p>Preparing of your application may be carried out
                                                                    electronically where we will prepare your completed
                                                                    application for you to download and print out, or by
                                                                    post where we will prepare and send your completed
                                                                    application to you by secure post.</p>

                                                                <div class="detailed-service-section-exclusive">
                                                                    <div class="devmarker">&nbsp;</div>

                                                                    <h2 class="subheader-price-section">Exclusive Visa
                                                                        Services for citizens of <span
                                                                                class="citizenship" data-citizenship="">specific countries</span>
                                                                    </h2>

                                                                    <p class="introduce-text">The following visa
                                                                        services are provided under a special visa
                                                                        simplification agreement between Russia and
                                                                        <span class="citizenship" data-citizenship="">specific country</span>.
                                                                        Using this method, there is only one processing
                                                                        time at the consulate of 6 working days for
                                                                        single and double entry visas, and 11 working
                                                                        days for multiple entry visas. As the Letter of
                                                                        Invitation only takes one day to issue the whole
                                                                        process is far quicker and cheaper than standard
                                                                        visa processing.</p>

