                                                                <h2 class="subheader-price-section">Standard Visa
                                                                    Services</h2>

                                                                <p>Processing of standard visa services includes any
                                                                    required Letter of invitation. The visa support
                                                                    documents, depending on the type of visa required,
                                                                    take the Russian authorities between 8 and 18
                                                                    working days to issue. Please note that during the
                                                                    processing of the visa support documents we do not
                                                                    need your passport, only a copy of your passport
                                                                    photo page. Once we have received the visa support
                                                                    documents from Russia, you can apply for a visa on
                                                                    either a standard (6 to 21 working days) or express
