                                <div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DNN_HTML DnnModule-8140"><a name="8140"></a>

                                    <div class="panel-group rr-margined-block">
                                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                                <h3 class="panel-title">
                                                    <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapsible-8140">
                                                        <span id="dnn_ctr8140_dnnTITLE_titleLabel" class="Head">Are there any external issues which may affect my visa processing?</span>


                                                    </a>
                                                </h3>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="collapsible-8140" class="panel-collapse collapse ">
                                                <div class="panel-body">
                                                    <div id="dnn_ctr8140_ContentPane"><!-- Start_Module_8140 -->
                                                        <div id="dnn_ctr8140_ModuleContent"
                                                             class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC">
                                                            <div id="dnn_ctr8140_HtmlModule_lblContent" class="Normal">
                                                                <p>The Russian authorities as well as the Russian
                                                                    Consulate may occasionally experience delays when
                                                                    issuing the visa support documents and visas
                                                                    (especially during spring, summer and New Year
                                                                    around Russian national holidays). For that reason,
                                                                    the visa due dates indicated on the order form are
                                                                    only provisional and by no means definitive. In any
                                                                    event, we do not recommend booking your flight or
                                                                    make other travel arrangements until you have got
                                                                    your passport and visa with you.</p>

                                                                <p>Please see the following link for any processing
                                                                    issues which may be affecting the Russian business
                                                                    visa service.</p>

                                                                <ul class="arrow">
                                                                    <li><a href="https://realrussia.co.uk/Info/ServiceStatus">Service status
                                                                            page</a></li>
                                                                </ul>

                                                            </div>


                                                        </div><!-- End_Module_8140 --></div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DNN_HTML DnnModule-8141"><a name="8141"></a>

                                    <div class="panel-group rr-margined-block">
                                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                                <h3 class="panel-title">
                                                    <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapsible-8141">
                                                        <span id="dnn_ctr8141_dnnTITLE_titleLabel" class="Head">How much will it cost?</span>


                                                    </a>
                                                </h3>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="collapsible-8141" class="panel-collapse collapse ">
                                                <div class="panel-body">
                                                    <div id="dnn_ctr8141_ContentPane"><!-- Start_Module_8141 -->
                                                        <div id="dnn_ctr8141_ModuleContent"
                                                             class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC">
                                                            <div id="dnn_ctr8141_HtmlModule_lblContent" class="Normal">
                                                                <p>The prices shown above include all fees, costs and
                                                                    charges to process and issue your visa, nothing is
                                                                    hidden, the price you see is the price you pay.</p>

                                                                <p>While our service fees are fixed, the consular fees
                                                                    and other costs are dependent upon your nationality,
                                                                    how quickly you need your visa, how long you are
                                                                    prepared for your passport to be at the consulate,
                                                                    how many entries you need and how long you need your
                                                                    visa valid for.</p>
                                                            </div>


                                                        </div><!-- End_Module_8141 --></div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DNN_HTML DnnModule-8142"><a name="8142"></a>

                                    <div class="panel-group rr-margined-block">
                                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                                <h3 class="panel-title">
                                                    <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapsible-8142">
                                                        <span id="dnn_ctr8142_dnnTITLE_titleLabel" class="Head">What is the Processing time?</span>


                                                    </a>
                                                </h3>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="collapsible-8142" class="panel-collapse collapse ">
                                                <div class="panel-body">
                                                    <div id="dnn_ctr8142_ContentPane"><!-- Start_Module_8142 -->
                                                        <div id="dnn_ctr8142_ModuleContent"
                                                             class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC">
                                                            <div id="dnn_ctr8142_HtmlModule_lblContent" class="Normal">
                                                                <p><span class="anchor"
                                                                         id="proctimes"><!-- options --></span></p>

                                                                <p>The <strong>visa support processing time</strong> is
                                                                    calculated in business days, excludes weekends and
                                                                    the day of order. The visa due dates indicated on
                                                                    the order form account for UK and <a
                                                                            href="https://realrussia.co.uk/Info/Faq#faq18">Russian public
                                                                        holidays</a>. However please note that the
                                                                    Russian authorities as well as the Russian consulate
                                                                    usually experience delays shortly after their
                                                                    holiday period is over which extends the processing
                                                                    time beyond these dates. For more details, please
                                                                    see section &ldquo;Are there any external issues
                                                                    which may affect my visa processing?</p>

                                                                <p>The visa support processing time refers to a number
                                                                    of working days that it will take us to issue your
                                                                    visa support documents once we have submitted your
                                                                    application to the Russian authorities. Remember, we
                                                                    can only start processing your application once you
                                                                    have paid and sent us a clear scan or fax of your
                                                                    passport photo page.</p>

                                                                <p>While we endeavour to process the orders as quickly
                                                                    as possible, you should note that orders made after
                                                                    13.00 GMT for telexes and 16.30 GMT for all other
                                                                    types of visa support will be processed the
                                                                    following working day only.</p>

                                                                <p><strong>Please note</strong> that:</p>

                                                                <ul>
                                                                    <li>The Russian authorities <strong>will
                                                                            not</strong> process applications for
                                                                        invitations for business and multiple entry visa
                                                                        support documents <strong>earlier than</strong>
                                                                        specific dates for different types of
                                                                        invitation:

                                                                        <ol>
                                                                            <li style="list-style-type: decimal;">For 12
                                                                                working day TELEX and 4-6 working day
                                                                                TELEX they will not process them earlier
                                                                                than 45 calendar days from the start
                                                                                date requested. Today we are able to
                                                                                submit these visa support documents for
                                                                                processing that have a start date
                                                                                before: 25 November 2021.
                                                                            </li>
                                                                            <li style="list-style-type: decimal;">For
                                                                                multiple entry 18, 14 and 12 working day
                                                                                (not telex) and 12, 8 and 5 working day
                                                                                single / double entry invitation they
                                                                                will not process them earlier than 90
                                                                                calendar days from the start date
                                                                                requested. Today we are able to submit
                                                                                these visa support documents for
                                                                                processing that have a start date
                                                                                before: 09 January 2022.
                                                                            </li>
                                                                            <!--<li style="list-style-type:decimal">For multiple entry 12 working day (not telex) and 5 working day single / double entry invitation they will not process them earlier than 90 calendar days from the start date requested.Today we are able to submit these visa support documents for processing that have a start date before: 09 January 2022.</li>
<li style="list-style-type:decimal">One and two working day processing of business visa support documents is only available for those clients whose planned entry date to Russia is within two weeks of application, this means you should be planning to enter Russia on or before: 25 October 2021.</li>-->
                                                                        </ol>
                                                                    </li>
                                                                    <li>If you apply in advance of the start date
                                                                        applicable to processing the visa support
                                                                        documents, then we will hold your application
                                                                        and apply at the earliest opportunity or you may
                                                                        change the start date to get the visa processing
                                                                        earlier.
                                                                    </li>
                                                                    <li>Please bear this in mind when choosing the
                                                                        appropriate business visa support service level.
                                                                        If you require further information, please <a
                                                                                href="https://realrussia.co.uk/Info/Contact-Us">contact our visa
                                                                            team</a> and we will be happy to help.
                                                                    </li>
                                                                    <li>If you are applying for a multiple entry visa
                                                                        then the original invitation will be sent by
                                                                        courier from Russia to our London office and
                                                                        assuming we have all of your other documents the
                                                                        visa application will be lodged at the consulate
                                                                        the next day. We assume a maximum delivery time
                                                                        of 3 working days and this is built into the
                                                                        expected dates shown as is the cost of the
                                                                        courier. Please note that delivery time does not
                                                                        apply to telex invitations which are sent
                                                                        electronically directly to the consulate.
                                                                    </li>
                                                                    <li>Please note: if you are travelling to the North
                                                                        Caucasus area (including but not restricted to
                                                                        Vladikavkaz, Magas, Machatschkala, Pyatigorsk)
                                                                        it will take the consulate 21 working days to
                                                                        process your visa, including those requested as
                                                                        &quot;Next Day&quot; services.
                                                                    </li>
                                                                </ul>

                                                                <p>The <strong>Consular Processing Time</strong> is the
                                                                    number of processing days that it will take the
                                                                    Russian Consulate to issue your visa once we have
                                                                    lodged your application with them. We will lodge
                                                                    your application the next consular working day after
                                                                    your invitation (if we are arranging one) has been
                                                                    issued and received in our London office provided
                                                                    that we have got your documents and they are all in
                                                                    order and you are able to visit the Russian Visa
                                                                    Application Centre to give your biometric data
                                                                    (fingerprints) &ndash; please <a
                                                                            href="https://realrussia.co.uk/Visas/Russian/Biometric">click
                                                                        here</a> for more information.</p>

                                                                <p>So, to work out how many days your visa will take to
                                                                    process and obtain, add the visa support processing
                                                                    time, the consular processing time and any delivery
                                                                    time for the invitation together.</p>

                                                                <p><strong>Please note</strong> that we do not need your
                                                                    passport for the whole processing time, just the
                                                                    element where we need to submit it to the consulate.
                                                                    Depending upon the service you select this will be
                                                                    between 3 and 8 business days.</p>

                                                            </div>


                                                        </div><!-- End_Module_8142 --></div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DNN_HTML DnnModule-8143"><a name="8143"></a>

                                    <div class="panel-group rr-margined-block">
                                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                                <h3 class="panel-title">
                                                    <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapsible-8143">
                                                        <span id="dnn_ctr8143_dnnTITLE_titleLabel" class="Head">How long will my telex be at the consulate?</span>


                                                    </a>
                                                </h3>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="collapsible-8143" class="panel-collapse collapse ">
                                                <div class="panel-body">
                                                    <div id="dnn_ctr8143_ContentPane"><!-- Start_Module_8143 -->
                                                        <div id="dnn_ctr8143_ModuleContent"
                                                             class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC">
                                                            <div id="dnn_ctr8143_HtmlModule_lblContent" class="Normal">
                                                                <p>The telex will be available for use at the Russian
                                                                    consulate for 30 days after its date of issue. Your
                                                                    visa application needs to be submitted within this
                                                                    30 day window otherwise the telex validity will
                                                                    expire and you will need to reapply and pay for a
                                                                    new invitation.</p>

                                                                <p>Please be aware that telexes with a purpose of visit
                                                                    listed as &quot;Cultural Relations&quot; are not
                                                                    currently being processed by the Russian Ministry of
                                                                    Foreign Affairs.</p>

                                                                <p>For more information or any assistance required on
                                                                    this matter please <a href="https://realrussia.co.uk/Info/Contact-Us">contact
                                                                        us.</a></p>

                                                            </div>


                                                        </div><!-- End_Module_8143 --></div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DNN_HTML DnnModule-8144"><a name="8144"></a>

                                    <div class="panel-group rr-margined-block">
