                                                                    <select id="typeVSD" class=" form-control input-sm">
                                                                        <option value="1">paper invitation</option>
                                                                        <option value="2">TELEX</option>
                                                                        <option value="3">your own visa support
                                                                            documents
                                                                        </option>
                                                                    </select>
                                                                </div>

                                                                <div class="visas-documents-section"
                                                                     id="nationalityRequirements"></div>
                                                            </div>


                                                        </div><!-- End_Module_8144 --></div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DNN_HTML DnnModule-8145"><a name="8145"></a>

                                    <div class="panel-group rr-margined-block">
                                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                                <h3 class="panel-title">
                                                    <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapsible-8145">
                                                        <span id="dnn_ctr8145_dnnTITLE_titleLabel" class="Head">How long can I stay in Russia using my visa?</span>


                                                    </a>
                                                </h3>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="collapsible-8145" class="panel-collapse collapse ">
                                                <div class="panel-body">
                                                    <div id="dnn_ctr8145_ContentPane"><!-- Start_Module_8145 -->
                                                        <div id="dnn_ctr8145_ModuleContent"
                                                             class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC">
                                                            <div id="dnn_ctr8145_HtmlModule_lblContent" class="Normal">
                                                                <p>Generally you may stay in Russia only up to the
                                                                    maximum validity period of the visa.</p>
                                                                <p>Please note that effective 01.06.07 according to new
                                                                    laws dependent upon your nationality there may be
                                                                    restrictions on how long you can stay in Russia
                                                                    within specific periods. This restriction, if it
                                                                    applies, will be written into the visa.</p>
                                                                <p>All nationalities are restricted to a maximum of 90
                                                                    days in a 180 day period when using a multiple entry
                                                                    visa.</p>
                                                            </div>


                                                        </div><!-- End_Module_8145 --></div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DNN_HTML DnnModule-8146"><a name="8146"></a>

                                    <div class="panel-group rr-margined-block">
                                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                                <h3 class="panel-title">
                                                    <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapsible-8146">
                                                        <span id="dnn_ctr8146_dnnTITLE_titleLabel" class="Head">Can I use a business visa for non-business purposes?</span>


                                                    </a>
                                                </h3>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="collapsible-8146" class="panel-collapse collapse ">
                                                <div class="panel-body">
                                                    <div id="dnn_ctr8146_ContentPane"><!-- Start_Module_8146 -->
                                                        <div id="dnn_ctr8146_ModuleContent"
                                                             class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC">
                                                            <div id="dnn_ctr8146_HtmlModule_lblContent" class="Normal">
                                                                <p>The purpose of visit requested for your visa should
                                                                    generally correspond with your initial visit
                                                                    intentions. The purpose of visit will be written on
                                                                    the visa support documents and encoded into your
                                                                    visa. However, this does not restrict you to this
                                                                    purpose and you may, for example, use a business
                                                                    visa to also visit family or friends or use a
                                                                    cultural visa to subsequently visit Russia for
                                                                    business purposes. However, if you are only
                                                                    considering a single trip of up to 30 days within a
                                                                    twelve month period, it may be more cost effective
                                                                    to consider a <a href="https://realrussia.co.uk/Visas/Russian/Tourist">tourist
                                                                        visa</a>.</p>

                                                            </div>


                                                        </div><!-- End_Module_8146 --></div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DNN_HTML DnnModule-8147"><a name="8147"></a>

                                    <div class="panel-group rr-margined-block">
                                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                                <h3 class="panel-title">
                                                    <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapsible-8147">
                                                        <span id="dnn_ctr8147_dnnTITLE_titleLabel" class="Head">Biometric data collection for Russian visas</span>


                                                    </a>
                                                </h3>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="collapsible-8147" class="panel-collapse collapse ">
                                                <div class="panel-body">
                                                    <div id="dnn_ctr8147_ContentPane"><!-- Start_Module_8147 -->
                                                        <div id="dnn_ctr8147_ModuleContent"
                                                             class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC">
                                                            <div id="dnn_ctr8147_HtmlModule_lblContent" class="Normal">
                                                                <p>You are required to provide your biometric data
                                                                    (fingerprints) when applying for a Russian visa.&nbsp;</p>

                                                                <p>See our <strong><em>Russian biometrics</em></strong>
                                                                    page for more information on&nbsp;<a
                                                                            href="https://realrussia.co.uk/Visas/Russian/Biometric">how the
                                                                        Russian visa biometric process works</a>&nbsp;and
                                                                    where to submit your fingerprints.</p>

                                                            </div>


                                                        </div><!-- End_Module_8147 --></div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DNN_HTML DnnModule-8148"><a name="8148"></a>

                                    <div class="panel-group rr-margined-block">
                                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                                <h3 class="panel-title">
                                                    <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapsible-8148">
                                                        <span id="dnn_ctr8148_dnnTITLE_titleLabel" class="Head">Do I need a visa for my child?</span>


                                                    </a>
                                                </h3>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="collapsible-8148" class="panel-collapse collapse ">
                                                <div class="panel-body">
                                                    <div id="dnn_ctr8148_ContentPane"><!-- Start_Module_8148 -->
                                                        <div id="dnn_ctr8148_ModuleContent"
                                                             class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC">
                                                            <div id="dnn_ctr8148_HtmlModule_lblContent" class="Normal">
                                                                <p>In most cases, a child can get an &lsquo;accompanying
                                                                    family member&rsquo; visa based on a parent&#39;s
                                                                    business visa. Please review the following
                                                                    information on <a href="https://realrussia.co.uk/Info/Faq#faq11">taking a
                                                                        child to Russia</a>.</p>

                                                            </div>


                                                        </div><!-- End_Module_8148 --></div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DNN_HTML DnnModule-8149"><a name="8149"></a>

                                    <div class="panel-group rr-margined-block">
                                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                                <h3 class="panel-title">
                                                    <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapsible-8149">
                                                        <span id="dnn_ctr8149_dnnTITLE_titleLabel" class="Head">Can you transfer a visa to a new passport for me?</span>


                                                    </a>
                                                </h3>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="collapsible-8149" class="panel-collapse collapse ">
                                                <div class="panel-body">
                                                    <div id="dnn_ctr8149_ContentPane"><!-- Start_Module_8149 -->
                                                        <div id="dnn_ctr8149_ModuleContent"
                                                             class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC">
                                                            <div id="dnn_ctr8149_HtmlModule_lblContent" class="Normal">
                                                                <p>If you have an active Russian visa in an expired or
                                                                    cancelled passport and wish to transfer this to a
                                                                    new passport then you will have to visit the Russian
                                                                    Visa Application Centre directly. Unfortunately, it
                                                                    cannot be done without your presence.</p>

                                                            </div>


                                                        </div><!-- End_Module_8149 --></div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DNN_HTML DnnModule-8150"><a name="8150"></a>

                                    <div class="panel-group rr-margined-block">
                                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                                <h3 class="panel-title">
                                                    <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapsible-8150">
                                                        <span id="dnn_ctr8150_dnnTITLE_titleLabel" class="Head">Can I deliver my passport and collect my visa from your office in person?</span>


                                                    </a>
                                                </h3>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="collapsible-8150" class="panel-collapse collapse ">
                                                <div class="panel-body">
                                                    <div id="dnn_ctr8150_ContentPane"><!-- Start_Module_8150 -->
                                                        <div id="dnn_ctr8150_ModuleContent"
                                                             class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC">
                                                            <div id="dnn_ctr8150_HtmlModule_lblContent" class="Normal">
                                                                <p>Yes, of course you can, we have an office in central
                                                                    London and we will be happy to see you and assist
                                                                    with your application if needed. If you intend to
                                                                    deliver an application in person or collect your
                                                                    passport and visa we are open for collection and
                                                                    deliveries during the following times.</p>

                                                                <p>
