                                <div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DNN_HTML DnnModule-8152"><a name="8152"></a>

                                    <div class="panel-group rr-margined-block">
                                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                                <h3 class="panel-title">
                                                    <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapsible-8152">
                                                        <span id="dnn_ctr8152_dnnTITLE_titleLabel" class="Head">Sounds good, how do I get my visa?</span>


                                                    </a>
                                                </h3>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="collapsible-8152" class="panel-collapse collapse ">
                                                <div class="panel-body">
                                                    <div id="dnn_ctr8152_ContentPane"><!-- Start_Module_8152 -->
                                                        <div id="dnn_ctr8152_ModuleContent"
                                                             class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC">
                                                            <div id="dnn_ctr8152_HtmlModule_lblContent" class="Normal">
                                                                <p>To order your business visa on-line, simply click on
                                                                    the level of service you want from the <a
                                                                            href="#options">options above</a>.</p>
                                                            </div>


                                                        </div><!-- End_Module_8152 --></div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DNN_HTML DnnModule-8153"><a name="8153"></a>

                                    <div class="panel-group rr-margined-block">
                                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                                <h3 class="panel-title">
                                                    <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapsible-8153">
                                                        <span id="dnn_ctr8153_dnnTITLE_titleLabel" class="Head">What will happen when I click the service I want?</span>


                                                    </a>
                                                </h3>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="collapsible-8153" class="panel-collapse collapse ">
                                                <div class="panel-body">
                                                    <div id="dnn_ctr8153_ContentPane"><!-- Start_Module_8153 -->
                                                        <div id="dnn_ctr8153_ModuleContent"
                                                             class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC">
                                                            <div id="dnn_ctr8153_HtmlModule_lblContent" class="Normal">
                                                                <ul class="big_numbers">
                                                                    <li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 6px 2em; padding: 4px 20px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; position: relative;">
                                                                        &nbsp;
                                                                    </li>
                                                                    <li>When you select the visa type&nbsp;and service
                                                                        level you want from the&nbsp;<a href="#options">options
                                                                            above</a>&nbsp;we will ask you to fill in
                                                                        the visa application form.&nbsp;You will need to
                                                                        have your national insurance number and passport
                                                                        to hand. You will find helpful explanations from
                                                                        us throughout the form to help explain
                                                                        questions. Once you have completed the form you
                                                                        will be given the option to pay via credit or
                                                                        debit card.
                                                                    </li>
                                                                    <li>Our visa team will check through your
                                                                        application form to make sure everything is
                                                                        correct and get in touch if there are any
                                                                        queries
                                                                    </li>
                                                                    <li>You will need to come down to London to visit
                                                                        the Russian visa application centre to submit
                                                                        your application and give your fingerprints with
                                                                        your valid passport and a single passport sized
                                                                        photo. We can also take a passport photo in
                                                                        office for you for an additional fee. You will
                                                                        sign your completed application form in office
                                                                        and our team will guide you through the process
                                                                        ready for when you arrive at the visa
                                                                        application centre.&nbsp;
                                                                    </li>
                                                                </ul>

                                                                <p>&nbsp;</p>

                                                                <ul class="big_numbers">
                                                                    <li><strong>That&#39;s it, that&#39;s all you have
                                                                            to do!</strong></li>
                                                                    <li>During the processing of your application, we
                                                                        will be on hand to answer any queries the
                                                                        Consulate may have and to ensure that your
                                                                        application is dealt with in a timely and
                                                                        efficient manner.
                                                                    </li>
                                                                    <li>The day your visa is ready we will collect it in
                                                                        person and return this to you using Royal Mail
                                                                        Special Delivery so you will have it the next
                                                                        business day before 1.00 pm.
                                                                    </li>
                                                                </ul>

                                                                <p>&nbsp;</p>

                                                                <p>You can follow the progress of your order through our
                                                                    online order tracking system which will detail the
                                                                    steps taken and the steps remaining to obtain your
                                                                    visa.</p>

                                                                <p>&nbsp;</p>

                                                                <p>Remember, when you are in Russia, please ensure that
                                                                    you <a href="https://realrussia.co.uk/Visas/Russian/Registration">register
                                                                        your visa</a>.</p>

                                                            </div>


                                                        </div><!-- End_Module_8153 --></div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DNN_HTML DnnModule-8154"><a name="8154"></a>

                                    <div class="panel-group rr-margined-block">
                                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                                <h3 class="panel-title">
                                                    <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapsible-8154">
                                                        <span id="dnn_ctr8154_dnnTITLE_titleLabel" class="Head">Are there any specifications for the passport photo?</span>


                                                    </a>
                                                </h3>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="collapsible-8154" class="panel-collapse collapse ">
                                                <div class="panel-body">
                                                    <div id="dnn_ctr8154_ContentPane"><!-- Start_Module_8154 -->
                                                        <div id="dnn_ctr8154_ModuleContent"
                                                             class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC">
                                                            <div id="dnn_ctr8154_HtmlModule_lblContent" class="Normal">
                                                                <span class="anchor" id="photo"><!-- photo details anchor --></span>
                                                                <p>The Russian consulate require that the photograph
                                                                    provided meet the following specifications:</p>

                                                                <ol>
                                                                    <li>It is a clear colour passport type photograph
                                                                        (black and white pictures are not acceptable)
                                                                    </li>
                                                                    <li>No older than six months</li>
                                                                    <li>Taken against a plain white background</li>
                                                                    <li>Printed on photographic paper (camera print)
                                                                    </li>
                                                                    <li>The frame size must be 35mm x 45mm</li>
                                                                    <li>The photo must show full front view of the head,
                                                                        with the face in the middle, and include the top
                                                                        of the shoulders
                                                                    </li>
                                                                    <li>Non-smiling, mouth closed, without sunglasses,
                                                                        hat/ cap or other head covering unless the
                                                                        applicant wears such items because of their
                                                                        religious beliefs or ethnic background
                                                                    </li>
                                                                </ol>

                                                            </div>


                                                        </div><!-- End_Module_8154 --></div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DNN_HTML DnnModule-8155"><a name="8155"></a>

                                    <div class="panel-group rr-margined-block">
                                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                                <h3 class="panel-title">
                                                    <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapsible-8155">
                                                        <span id="dnn_ctr8155_dnnTITLE_titleLabel" class="Head">How do I read my visa?</span>


                                                    </a>
                                                </h3>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="collapsible-8155" class="panel-collapse collapse ">
                                                <div class="panel-body">
                                                    <div id="dnn_ctr8155_ContentPane"><!-- Start_Module_8155 -->
                                                        <div id="dnn_ctr8155_ModuleContent"
                                                             class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC">
                                                            <div id="dnn_ctr8155_HtmlModule_lblContent" class="Normal">
                                                                <p>Please see the following guide for more information:
                                                                    <a class="withBullets"
                                                                       href="https://realrussia.co.uk/Visas/Russian/RussianVisasExplained">Reading
                                                                        a Russian visa</a></p>
                                                                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                                                            </div>


                                                        </div><!-- End_Module_8155 --></div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DNN_HTML DnnModule-8156"><a name="8156"></a>

                                    <div class="panel-group rr-margined-block">
                                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                                <h3 class="panel-title">
                                                    <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapsible-8156">
                                                        <span id="dnn_ctr8156_dnnTITLE_titleLabel" class="Head">Emergency Assistance</span>


                                                    </a>
                                                </h3>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="collapsible-8156" class="panel-collapse collapse ">
                                                <div class="panel-body">
                                                    <div id="dnn_ctr8156_ContentPane"><!-- Start_Module_8156 -->
                                                        <div id="dnn_ctr8156_ModuleContent"
                                                             class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC">
                                                            <div id="dnn_ctr8156_HtmlModule_lblContent" class="Normal">
                                                                <p>If you&rsquo;re in need of assistance whilst
                                                                    travelling, we offer a dedicated 24 hour telephone
                                                                    support service.</p>

                                                                <p>For all emergencies you can call us on +44 (0) 207
                                                                    100 7370 where our operators are available to
                                                                    provide help 7 days a week, 365 days a year.</p>

                                                                <p>If you are a Real Russia TravelSim user, then calls
                                                                    to our helpline are free for the first three
                                                                    minutes. <a href="https://realrussia.co.uk/TravelSim">Click here</a> for
                                                                    more information on the Real Russia TravelSim.</p>

                                                                <p><span style="line-height: 1.6;">If you experience problems whilst away, our team can offer guidance and support. If for example you have mislaid your passport, you are experiencing difficulty boarding a train or any number of other travel issues, call our emergency helpline for immediate assistance.</span>
                                                                </p>

                                                                <p>&nbsp;</p>

                                                            </div>


                                                        </div><!-- End_Module_8156 --></div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DNN_HTML DnnModule-8157"><a name="8157"></a>

                                    <div class="panel-group rr-margined-block">
                                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                                <h3 class="panel-title">
                                                    <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapsible-8157">
                                                        <span id="dnn_ctr8157_dnnTITLE_titleLabel" class="Head">Can you tell me more?</span>


                                                    </a>
                                                </h3>
                                            </div>
